  <description type="morphology">Stems to 1 cm.  Leaves 0.7–0.9 mm, ligulate to short-lanceolate, bordered distally by 1–5 rows of less papillose, thick-walled cells; apex broadly acute; costa ending 2–4 cells before the apex, abaxially papillose; distal laminal cells 10–12 µm wide, 1:1, walls thin in medial portion of leaf, lumens quadrate, proximal cells thin-walled throughout.</description>
